    http://www.opentravel.org/OTM/Common/v0

    ValueWithAttributes URL

      • http://www.opentravel.org/OTM/Common/v0:URL

      • Description

        Web site address, in IETF specified format.
        Additional Documentation 
        Type Value
        Implementers Assigned XSD Type: {http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema}anyURI

    • Example XML

      <?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="yes"?>

<URL defaultInd="true" type="I am a short string." xmlns="http://www.opentravel.org/OTM/Common/v0">http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema</URL>

      Example JSON

      {
  "URL" : {
    "value" : "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema",
    "type" : "I am a short string.",
    "defaultInd" : true
  }
}

      • Attribute Summary

        Attributes 
        Name Description
        type
        Defines the purpose of the URL address, such as personal, business, public, etc.
        Details
        Type http://www.opentravel.org/OTM/Common/v0:String_Short
        Example Value I am a short string.
        Required false
        Pattern N/A
        Max Occurrences 1

      • Indicator Summary

        Indicators 
        Name Description
        defaultInd
        Indicates whether or not this is the default URL.
